== 任內事蹟 ==
有效運用位處嘉老山的草屯鎮示範公墓，運用公共造產清償草屯鎮積欠之債務，並使鎮庫轉虧為盈。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180328004076-260407?chdtv|title=草屯鎮長洪國浩理財高手 財政總盈餘4.3億餘元|author=楊樹煌|date=2018-03-28|work=中國時報|publisher=|accessdate=|language=中文|format=}}</ref>

改建活化原先鎮立體育場後方之公墓為草屯植物公園。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-06-30/129570|title=墓仔埔變身公園！蔡英文讚草屯植物公園有創意|author=陳龍棋|date=2018-06-30|work=新頭殼|publisher=|accessdate=|language=中文|format=|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811071419/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-06-30/129570|dead-url=no}}</ref>

任內重新鋪設市區人行道，完成改善下水道建設。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/1254914|title=〈中部〉（南投）草屯道路重舖 中興路將完工|author=陳鳳麗|date=2018-12-19|work=自由時報|publisher=|accessdate=|language=中文|format=|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714064436/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/local/paper/1254914|dead-url=no}}</ref>

新建大成街停車場，並招商經營。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://udn.com/news/story/7325/3375424|title=草屯大成街停車場啟用 估年收500萬當「金雞母」|author=賴香珊|date=2018-09-19|work=聯合報|publisher=|accessdate=|language=中文|format=|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714064429/https://udn.com/news/story/7325/3375424|dead-url=no}}</ref>

尚無力解決鎮內垃圾堆積問題，因垃圾累積過多而數度引發民怨。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aloc/201805210331.aspx|title=沒有焚化爐燒垃圾 南投縣堆積出民怨|author=吳哲豪|date=2018-05-21|work=中央通訊社|publisher=|accessdate=|language=中文|format=|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714064435/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aloc/201805210331.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

